{"tid":970831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撳錢撳得慢惹禍 39歲男捱打","createTime":"2019-01-06T07:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T16:59:17.000Z","uid":20058,"like":598,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"f97b590a03a97e487fde89fa4631032872604063","tid":970831,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"一名39歲男子凌晨在旺角好望角大廈一銀行櫃員機提款期間，疑因為佔用時間太久，惹起隨後排隊的另一名男子不滿，雙方互罵後，事主疑遭對方揮拳打傷頭部。<br />\n<br />\n現場為旺角彌敦道618號好望角大廈。警方凌晨2時28分接獲事主報案，指與一名男子因瑣事爭執，其間該名男子懷疑以手襲擊事主後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，案件列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，暫未有人被捕，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進，正追緝一名年約30歲，身高約1.6米，中等身材，案發時身穿黑色上衣，黑色長褲的男子。而事主頭部受傷，清醒送廣華醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1403814/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1403814%2F&d=X4%2FzfWi5cbJ7qy%2BCoL4PzS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8c1d3f2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1403814%2F&h=be903b71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1403814/</a>"},{"pid":"f5754bdf5aa4fc21a464df3852f11855c5075693","tid":970831,"uid":47492,"like":422,"dislike":1,"score":421,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"條垃圾肯定出完又入"},{"pid":"d3380770e157df1df4d0364e58b6389512a117d9","tid":970831,"uid":63154,"like":370,"dislike":1,"score":369,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"打得好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eb898b79aded8492335e594c5ac584773d5520","tid":970831,"uid":54930,"like":6,"dislike":97,"score":-91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾，大家都係男人有咩好打"},{"pid":"ded5d8c7ffddfe288cfe969ed0d54a4cfa206664","tid":970831,"uid":52459,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"抵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0783475d5c9409a6259a0d395c4b87b59007db","tid":97